[{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0033","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0033.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1469","title":"Joomla! JProject Manager 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 JProject Manager 组件（com_jprojectmanager）1.0 版本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数传递包含 `../` 序列的特制请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件，可能导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞源于组件对用户输入路径过滤不严，无需身份认证即可利用，影响所有使用该组件的 Joomla! 站点。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1469"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-19T19:30:00.710","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:27.293","remediation":"该组件已停止维护且无官方补丁，建议立即在 Joomla 后台卸载并移除 com_jprojectmanager 组件，或删除服务器上对应目录。如业务必须使用，可在 .htaccess 中添加规则过滤 controller 参数中的 \"../\" 路径遍历字符，或修改组件源码对 controller 参数做 basename 校验。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlajprojectmanager-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39282","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12146","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39383","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12146","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1469.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1469.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1469.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1469.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-1469-1646.yaml","https://github.com/amad3us47/amad3us47.github.io/blob/07cfc0edf465277028554b47198f6f186d3215b6/data/cve-2010-1469-1648.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1469_19.yaml","https://github.com/1in9e/gosint/blob/bdda4461515c4398c08638676bbbfe451b73ff95/client/vuln_scan/nuclei/tools/nuclei-templates/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1469.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1469-1647.yaml","https://github.com/elijah-bennett0/IntentLimit/blob/bcfe225cf61ee454aa53896f7f3120246f52119f/tools/exploitation/CrazyIngrate/exploits/cve_2010_1469/cve_2010_1469.py","https://github.com/thompson005/nuclei-scanner/blob/6b5cfd844640c882a3d278f76f395a74ee14ef81/nucleivault/cve/cve-2010-1469.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0033.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0034","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0034.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1470","title":"Joomla! Web TV 组件本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Web TV 组件（com_webtv）1.0 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，由于程序对 index.php 中 controller 参数未做充分的路径过滤，远程攻击者可通过构造包含 ..（点点）的恶意路径序列绕过限制，读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响使用此组件的 Joomla! 网站，攻击无需身份认证，仅需发送特制 HTTP 请求即可触发，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，可能导致敏感信息泄露等严重后果。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1470"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-19T19:30:00.743","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:27.400","remediation":"立即卸载 Joomla! 组件 com_webtv 1.0，该组件已停止维护且无官方补丁。如必须使用，在 index.php 入口文件添加 `$controller = basename($controller);` 过滤路径遍历，或在 .htaccess 中禁用 `controller` 参数的点号传值：`RewriteCond %{QUERY_STRING} controller=\\.\\./ [NC]` 并返回 403。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlawebtv-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39405","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12166","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/0858","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12166","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1470.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1470.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1470.yaml","https://github.com/swisskyrepo/PayloadsAllTheThings/blob/c142771628ecb898b35da26d37270770e457f0e0/File%20Inclusion/README.md","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1470-1653.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2ada0fed8a5975a1e69890298da5128a1d96babb/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1470.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-1470_1.yaml","https://github.com/u21h2/nacs/blob/1eaa239ded7496317a47073605c8ddda70686ef5/web/poc/pocs/nuclei/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1470.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/06/Artifact/Report.csv","https://github.com/B0rn2beR00T/Pentester_Cheatsheet/blob/f1e1f80ebf2039a5e4e47d705f8dbb04a048052f/Web_Vuln/File_Inclusion_checklist.md","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2010/README.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0034.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0035","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0035.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1471","title":"Joomla AddressBook 组件 1.5.0 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 AddressBook 组件（com_addressbook）1.5.0 版本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 文件的 controller 参数传入 `..` 路径序列，绕过访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，攻击复杂度低。受影响的组件广泛应用于各类 Joomla! 站点，危害等级高，CVSS 评分 7.5。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1471"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-19T19:30:00.790","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:27.510","remediation":"立即卸载 com_addressbook 组件，该组件 1.5.0 及更早版本已多年无人维护且无安全补丁。在 wp-content/plugins/ 或 components/ 目录下检查并删除相关文件。如业务依赖该功能，建议使用受支持的替代插件或自行在入口文件中对 controller 参数进行严格过滤，拒绝包含 `../` 等目录遍历字符的输入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlaaddressbook-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39412","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12170","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/0862","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12170","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1471.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1471.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1471.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1471.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-1471-1657.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1471-1655.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2ada0fed8a5975a1e69890298da5128a1d96babb/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1471.json","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/yaml/Joomla/CVE-2010-1471.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1471_25.yaml","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-reserve/blob/c1581dbabe569bc0543baa46ed25f8fdd1555b2b/nvd/2010/CVE-2010-1471.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-1471_1.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0035.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0036","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0036.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1472","title":"Joomla! Daily Horoscope 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Daily Horoscope 组件 1.5.0 版本存在目录遍历漏洞（CWE-22）。远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数传递 `../` 序列，利用路径遍历读取服务器上的任意文件，如配置文件、敏感数据等。该漏洞无需身份认证，攻击条件简单，危害等级高，影响所有使用该组件的 Joomla! 站点。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1472"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-19T19:30:00.820","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:27.617","remediation":"立即卸载或禁用 Daily Horoscope (com_horoscope) 1.5.0 组件，该组件已停止维护且无官方补丁。如业务必须使用，在 Web 服务器层面添加规则拦截 `controller` 参数中的 `../` 序列，或在 Joomla! 全局输入过滤中启用路径遍历字符清理作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlahoroscope-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39406","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12167","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/0859","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12167","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1472.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1472.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1472.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1472.js","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-1472-1661.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1472-1660.yaml","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_iddirtra","https://github.com/cyb3r-w0lf/nuclei-template-collection/blob/7025ebe04ab60b84aee0af1ecf4f90601332e8e7/nuclei-templates/CVE-2010/cve-2010-1472.yaml","https://github.com/u21h2/nacs/blob/1eaa239ded7496317a47073605c8ddda70686ef5/web/poc/pocs_dev/nucleibak/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1472.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2010-1472-1660.yaml","https://github.com/Jimi-Lab/workflow/blob/64e0ded287550d9a2309e6b5a8188e373d9e88ca/VulnVersion/DataSet/CveDetail/CVE-2022-0847/cxsecurity/list.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0036.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0037","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0037.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1473","title":"Joomla! Advertising 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Advertising 组件（版本 0.25）存在目录遍历漏洞，该漏洞源于对 controller 参数缺乏充分的过滤检查。远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 传递包含 `../` 等目录跳转序列的特制请求，实现任意文件读取，可能导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞攻击复杂度较低，无需身份认证即可利用。CVSS 评分 6.8，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1473"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-19T19:30:00.850","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:27.727","remediation":"立即卸载 Joomla! 的 Advertising (com_advertising) 组件 0.25 版本，该组件已不再维护且存在目录遍历漏洞。作为替代方案，使用其他受支持的广告管理扩展。如无法卸载，在服务器层面限制 index.php 的 controller 参数仅允许白名单值，并禁用 .. 路径遍历。更新 Joomla! 核心至最新版本以启用内置安全机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlaeasyadbanner-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39410","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12171","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12171","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1473.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1473.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1473.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2ada0fed8a5975a1e69890298da5128a1d96babb/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1473.json","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-1473-1666.yaml","https://github.com/TheMirkin/CVE-List-Public-Exploits/blob/f496d51148a2b151f14fe6d0bef5b42ee27f6ccb/CVE%20List/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1473.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1473_33.yaml","https://github.com/baric6/ThreatHunting/blob/fa3a6cd3a5755f5dc3018997186ddb7b76717945/cvePoC_2010.json","https://github.com/TonyStark1109/JARVIS-MARK-5/blob/756e6a7362ebce8a56e07f16413733ad23d90c7a/nuclei-templates/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1473.yaml","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/f2d12f176efdb99f18928b2678d34b7fa4f530f8/content/CVE-2010-1473.md","https://github.com/hack007x/veil_poc/blob/5cfe1da6e975ba816d728597885a5c5e79bda8bd/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1473.poc"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0037.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0038","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0038.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1474","title":"Joomla! Sweetykeeper 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Sweety Keeper 组件（com_sweetykeeper）1.5.x 版本存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向 index.php 文件的 controller 参数传入 `../` 序列绕过路径限制，读取服务器上的任意文件，可能导致敏感信息泄露（如配置文件、系统文件等）。该漏洞源于对用户输入的 controller 参数缺乏充分的过滤与验证，CWE-22 目录遍历类型，CVSS 评分 6.8，危害等级中危。建议升级至受影响版本的补丁或替代组件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1474"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-19T19:30:00.883","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:27.833","remediation":"该漏洞源于 Joomla! 第三方扩展 Sweety Keeper 1.5.x（com_sweetykeeper）中 controller 参数缺乏路径过滤，允许远程攻击者通过 ../ 目录遍历读取任意文件。由于该组件已停止维护，推荐在 Joomla! 后台扩展管理中卸载该组件。如需保留功能，修改组件源码 controller 入口文件对 controller 参数执行 basename() 过滤和路径白名单校验，并在 .htaccess 中添加 RewriteCond %{QUERY_STRING} controller=.*\\.\\./ 拦截规则。同时在 WAF（如 ModSecurity）中部署规则阻止包含 ../ 的 controller 参数请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlasweetykeeper-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39388","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12182","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39399","https://exchange.xforc