atus":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T15:18:49.780232661+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2010-1955","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12868"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12868"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0075.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0029","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0029.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1353","title":"Joomla LoginBox Pro 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Wowjoomla 公司的 Joomla! 组件 LoginBox Pro 中存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 文件的 view 参数传递包含 `..`（点点）的恶意字符串，绕过目录限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响使用该组件的 Joomla! 网站，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。攻击无需身份认证，利用难度较低，可导致敏感信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1353"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-12T18:30:01.007","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:11.527","remediation":"立即卸载 LoginBox Pro (com_loginbox) 组件，该组件已停止维护且无安全更新。如必须使用，在 Joomla! 全局配置中启用「输入过滤」并将 view 参数加入黑名单，拦截 `../` 等路径遍历字符。同时在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）层面添加重写规则，拒绝包含 `../` 的 view 参数请求。作为临时缓解措施，可通过 WAF 规则拦截 `index.php?option=com_loginbox&view=.*\\.\\..*` 模式的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlaloginbox-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39349","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12068","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39212","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/0808","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57533","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12068","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1353.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1353.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1353.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/ac